Title: Christmas Scavenger Hunt
Writer: George Klembith (Written by), Tammy Klembith (Written by)
Actors: Tom Arnold, Kevin McGarry, Kim Shaw, Pip Dwyer
Plot: When Belinda (Kim Shaw) heads back to her hometown for the holidays, things get complicated when she is forced to team up with her ex, Dustin (Kevin McGarry), at the town's annual Christmas scavenger hunt.
